  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/763a239eb00c651e92ac88b686697559.avif?t=1764106481\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br><br>A Castle Full of Cats is a hidden object game with a metroidvania structure: alternate paths, keys to be found, mysterious NPC's and so much more!<br><br>Fofiño found himself cursed by an evil force and had transformed every cat in the castle into a dark (yet cute) creature. <br>Now only Lily can save her soulmate and release the castle from the spell!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/580b774aad850a6d89714570ee4926e4.poster.avif?t=1764106481\" width=614 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/580b774aad850a6d89714570ee4926e4.webm?t=1764106481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/580b774aad850a6d89714570ee4926e4.mp4?t=1764106481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>600+ cats<br></li><li>20+ unique rooms<br></li><li>100+ hidden cats<br></li><li>Secrets!!!<br></li><li>Steam achievements</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/763a239eb00c651e92ac88b686697559.avif?t=1764106481\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br><br>A Castle Full of Cats is a hidden object game with a metroidvania structure: alternate paths, keys to be found, mysterious NPC's and so much more!<br><br>Fofiño found himself cursed by an evil force and had transformed every cat in the castle into a dark (yet cute) creature. <br>Now only Lily can save her soulmate and release the castle from the spell!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/580b774aad850a6d89714570ee4926e4.poster.avif?t=1764106481\" width=614 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/580b774aad850a6d89714570ee4926e4.webm?t=1764106481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070550/extras/580b774aad850a6d89714570ee4926e4.mp4?t=1764106481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>600+ cats<br></li><li>20+ unique rooms<br></li><li>100+ hidden cats<br></li><li>Secrets!!!<br></li><li>Steam achievements</li></ul>",
